In a statement issued on May 5, 2019, the speaker sends greetings and best wishes to all those celebrating Cinco de Mayo. The statement recognizes the historic Battle of Puebla, where Mexican forces triumphed over the French army on May 5, 1862. The courage and patriotism of the Mexican soldiers are celebrated, as well as the contributions of Mexican Americans to the nation. The speaker, Melania and I, hope those celebrating enjoy the festivities.